Lemma doGenericServer_lastApplied: forall (h : name) (st : raft_data) (out : list raft_output) (st' : raft_data) (ms : list (name * msg)), doGenericServer h st = (out, st', ms) -> lastApplied st' <= max (lastApplied st) (commitIndex st).
